description: The patient started to display symptoms after returning from Tenerife - a Group B country.
title: Coronavirus: Guernsey has first confirmed case
title_page: Coronavirus: Guernsey has first confirmed case - BBC News
maintext: The school said the child was not with their parent in Tenerife and while symptomless, they were self-isolating at home with guidance from Public Health England on how to isolate further from their parents.
